/*

all legal RegExp

/a/
(/a/)
[/a/]
[12, /a/]

!/a/

+/a/
-/a/
* /a/
/ /a/
%/a/

===/a/
!==/a/
==/a/
!=/a/
>/a/
>=/a/
</a/
<=/a/

&/a/
|/a/
^/a/
~/a/
<</a/
>>/a/
>>>/a/

&&/a/
||/a/
?/a/
=/a/
,/a/

